Tuan Moon.

289
00:17:14,005 --> 00:17:17,202
Saya minta maaf kerana
buat masalah di depan pelanggan.

290
00:17:17,908 --> 00:17:18,908
Lupakan saja.

291
00:17:22,099 --> 00:17:23,099
Tuan Moon.

292
00:17:26,505 --> 00:17:28,301
Sejujurnya, saya
tak suka Baek Do Hong.

