Saya suka awak, bodoh.

294
00:17:31,305 --> 00:17:34,400
Wanita itu pura-pura
suka dan cintakan kamu.

295
00:17:34,598 --> 00:17:36,010
Tapi dia cuma gunakan kamu.

296
00:17:37,908 --> 00:17:39,440
Kenapa Baek Do Hong?

297
00:17:39,809 --> 00:17:42,360
Dia serius sampai luahkan perasaan
kepada awak di depan orang.

298
00:17:42,799 --> 00:17:43,799
Awak gunakan dia?

299
00:17:44,519 --> 00:17:45,519
Apa?

300
