Awak ini...

332
00:19:41,720 --> 00:19:42,720
Serius.

333
00:19:44,110 --> 00:19:45,240
Tak guna.

334
00:19:51,512 --> 00:19:52,614
Shin Jae Rim!

335
00:19:53,603 --> 00:19:55,320
